### Fault Propagation Chain

```
ts-travel-service (HIGH_CPU/GC) ─┐
                                   ├──► ts-route-plan-service (MALFORMED_RESPONSE)
ts-seat-service (HIGH_CPU/GC)  ───┘         │
                                             │ null/empty data in HTTP 200
                                             ▼
                                  ts-travel-plan-service (HIGH_ERROR_RATE: 100% NPE)
                                             │
                                             │ HTTP 500 propagated
                                             ▼
                                  ts-ui-dashboard (HIGH_ERROR_RATE)
                                             │
                                             │ 20s timeout
                                             ▼
                                        loadgenerator (TIMEOUT)
```

**Root Cause**: `ts-route-plan-service` is returning HTTP 200 responses with null/empty `data` fields (triggered by increased traffic load causing 3.3x CPU and 5.4x GC pressure increase), and `ts-travel-plan-service` does not handle these null responses gracefully, resulting in 100% NullPointerException failure rate across all three travelPlan API endpoints.
